  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> wedges</strong> to a baking tray, drizzle them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>then season<strong> </strong>with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>smoked paprika </strong>(save the rest for later!) and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25 min until they're crisp – these are your <strong>paprika wedges</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1620230263704-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
