    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat</p><p>Slice the <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Once toasted, set aside until serving and reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
